item.title: !Ergent!How to?
item.dc:creator: @Maxie35 Maxie35
item.description:
@Maxie35 wrote:

In TextHandler.java search for what the tele tab says, then change it to what u want, to actually make u tele to that place first make a command to tele u to the place u want, then go to Client.java

Search for: case 168

In there u should see all custom commands, search for the one u tele to with the tab u want to change, then change it to the command u made.

And voila u got a new tele tab =)
